gameRecap.title: Game Recap: 76ers 126, Nuggets 121
gameRecap.excerpt: Joel Embiid leads the way with 41 points, seven rebounds and 10 assists as the 76ers defeat the Nuggets, 126-121.  Tyrese Maxey (25 points, five rebounds, nine assists) and Tobias Harris (24 points, five rebounds, four assists) added a combined 49 points in the victory.  Nikola Jokic tallied 25 points and 19 rebounds for the Nuggets, while Jamal Murray added 17 points and 10 assists in the losing effort.  The 76ers improve to 26-13 on the season, while the Nuggets fall to 28-14.
